<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Investment</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 60px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .greeting {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: left;
      color: #145A32;
    }

    .message {
      margin-top: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: block;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px 0;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 2px solid #145A32;
      color: #145A32;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #145A32;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .amount {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #d4af37;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img class="logo" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dpmx02shl/image/upload/v1741383995/logo_rujohq.png" alt="Logo" />
      <h4 class="greeting">Dear Investor <%= name %>,</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="message">
      <p>
        Thank you for your recent investment of <span class="amount">$<%= amount %></span> in our <span style="text-transform: capitalize;"><%= code %></span> Plan. Your Investment has been processed and your
        funds have been allocated to your chosen investment strategy. Kindly check back daily for your investment updates.
      </p>

      <p>
        We are committed to providing our investors with the highest level of
        service and support, and we are always here to answer any questions you
        may have. If you need assistance with your account or have any
        investment-related questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you again for choosing to invest with us.</p>
    </div>
    <a style="color: #145A32;" class="cta-button" href="https://www.fortuneholders.com/user/dashboard">Access Your Dashboard</a>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= year %>. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        For inquiries, please contact our support center at
        <a href="mailto:support@fortuneholders.com">support@fortuneholders.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>